    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "To resolve this error I just needed to install `@types/node` with a major version that matched my Node version. \r\n\r\nI.e. `node -v` returned `v14.18.1` so I added `\"@types/node\": \"14.17.34\",` (the last release of @types/node on major version 14) to my `packages.json` file and then `yarn` 🚀 ",
